iet-place-an-eerie-visit-to-the-empty-jordan-river/00000191-79a1-daab-a3f3-f9a306760000</guid></item><item><title>由于担心局势升级，达美航空取消十月底之前往返以色列的航班</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/delta-air-lines-cancels-israel-flights-until-end-of-october-amid-escalation-fears/00000191-7a66-dacb-afb3-fbff53310000</link><description>国际航空公司继续取消和推迟航班，其中一些航班推迟到 2025 年春季，但其他航空公司在真主党和伊朗安全威胁升级后已恢复航班</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 14:25:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/delta-air-lines-cancels-israel-flights-until-end-of-october-amid-escalation-fears/00000191-7a66-dacb-afb3-fbff53310000</guid></item><item><title>经历数月的水资源短缺后，以色列将在东耶路撒冷附近设立水站</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-set-up-water-stations-in-east-jerusalem-neighborhood-after-months-of-shortages/00000191-7a3b-d15d-a3d7-7e7be6200000</link><description>当局回应高等法院的请愿书称，他们调查了该社区，发现供水严重中断，迫使居民私下购买水在家中使用</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 14:21:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-to-set-up-water-stations-in-east-jerusalem-neighborhood-after-months-of-shortages/00000191-7a3b-d15d-a3d7-7e7be6200000</guid></item><item><title>以色列作家大卫·格罗斯曼荣获著名的海涅奖</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-author-david-grossman-wins-prestigious-heine-prize/00000191-7a10-d15d-a3d7-7e73467f0000</link><description>杜塞尔多夫市每两年颁发一次该奖项，其中包括 56,000 美元的现金奖励，格罗斯曼在得知该奖项的消息时表示，他很高兴“看到在以色列写下的东西被听到并表达了一些东西”</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 14:13:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-author-david-grossman-wins-prestigious-heine-prize/00000191-7a10-d15d-a3d7-7e73467f0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列大学因“声誉”担忧退出 10 月 7 日犹太-阿拉伯活动</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-college-backtracks-jewish-arab-event-marking-oct-7-citing-reputational-fears/00000191-79b4-d8d0-a7bb-f9b583450000</link><description>萨皮尔学术学院位于斯德罗特郊外，靠近加沙边境，已经确定了该活动的日期。 “这会如何玷污学院的名誉？”一名组织者问道，一名工作人员则批评领导层的“可悲决定”</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 12:12:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-college-backtracks-jewish-arab-event-marking-oct-7-citing-reputational-fears/00000191-79b4-d8d0-a7bb-f9b583450000</guid></item><item><title>斯莫特里奇经济学既不好也不坏，它们只是丑陋</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/smotrichomics-are-neither-good-nor-bad-theyre-just-ugly/00000191-79d2-dacb-afb3-f9fba5260000</link><description>以色列财政部长有比担心经济更重要的事情要做。但抱怨以牺牲明智政策为代价支持宗教和定居者的做法没有抓住要点</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 11:44:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/smotrichomics-are-neither-good-nor-bad-theyre-just-ugly/00000191-79d2-dacb-afb3-f9fba5260000</guid></item><item><title>埃及努力维持停火谈判，内塔尼亚胡和辛瓦尔缺乏退出加沙的战略</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-and-sinwar-lack-a-gaza-exit-strategy-as-egypt-fights-to-keep-talks-alive/00000191-79ac-dacb-afb3-f9bf55ed0000</link><description>以色列总理和哈马斯领导人的表现就好像他们有一篮子取之不尽的选择。在这种现实下，加沙的人质没有什么希望</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 11:39:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-and-sinwar-lack-a-gaza-exit-strategy-as-egypt-fights-to-keep-talks-alive/00000191-79ac-dacb-afb3-f9bf55ed0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列无人机袭击约旦河西岸图勒凯尔姆，造成三名巴勒斯坦人死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/three-palestinians-killed-by-israeli-drone-strike-in-west-banks-tulkarm-ministry-says/00000191-79b4-daab-a3f3-f9b61b0e0000</link><description>以色列军方表示，这架无人机的目标是一群对以色列国防军和辛贝特部队构成危险的武装人员，这些武装人员从周四开始在该市进行行动</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 11:07:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/three-palestinians-killed-by-israeli-drone-strike-in-west-banks-tulkarm-ministry-says/00000191-79b4-daab-a3f3-f9b61b0e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列陆军检察官：斯德泰曼士兵殴打、电击、鸡奸加沙被拘留者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/idf-prosecutor-sde-teiman-soldiers-beat-electrified-sodomized-gaza-detainee/00000191-796d-de08-a3f9-796f17e00000</link><description>上个月被捕的五名以色列国防军士兵被指控严重虐待一名巴勒斯坦被拘留者。军事检察官要求他们再软禁两周</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 10:42:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/idf-prosecutor-sde-teiman-soldiers-beat-electrified-sodomized-gaza-detainee/00000191-796d-de08-a3f9-796f17e00000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队逮捕了四名西岸嫌疑人，罪名是“针对巴勒斯坦人的恐怖行为”，其中包括在吉特发生致命暴行</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-forces-arrest-four-west-bank-suspects-for-terrorist-acts-against-palestinians/00000191-7936-d2f3-afdf-7dffd68d0000</link><description>这是与巴勒斯坦西岸吉特村定居者骚乱有关的首次逮捕，一名巴勒斯坦人被杀</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 09:56:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/israeli-forces-arrest-four-west-bank-suspects-for-terrorist-acts-against-palestinians/00000191-7936-d2f3-afdf-7dffd68d0000</guid></item><item><title>如果与哈马斯和真主党的消耗战继续下去，以色列将在一年内崩溃</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-22/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-will-collapse-within-a-year-if-the-war-against-hamas-and-hezbollah-continues/00000191-795e-d8d0-a7bb-f9ff81000000</link><description></description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 09:44:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-22/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-will-collapse-within-a-year-if-the-war-against-hamas-and-hezbollah-continues/00000191-795e-d8d0-a7bb-f9ff81000000</guid></item><item><title>让煽动反对加沙人的立法者摆脱困境将使以色列在海牙付出代价</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/letting-lawmakers-who-incite-against-gazans-off-the-hook-will-cost-israel-in-the-hague/00000191-748f-dc26-a9d7-f49ffe910000</link><description>部长们和议会议员没有约束加沙“热血沸腾”的士兵，而是鼓励他们攻击巴勒斯坦平民。总检察长必须无视国家检察官不要调查他们的建议，但他的决定已经玷污了以色列的执法系统</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 09:35:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/letting-lawmakers-who-incite-against-gazans-off-the-hook-will-cost-israel-in-the-hague/00000191-748f-dc26-a9d7-f49ffe910000</guid></item><item><title>“粉碎哈马斯”与“带他们回家”：以色列人质如何成为丑陋政治游戏中的棋子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/how-israeli-hostages-became-pawns-in-an-ugly-political-game/00000191-75a1-d189-adbb-7dad718a0000</link><description>呼吁释放加沙人质的活动人士感到，这是他们核心民族身份的紧迫性，而以色列右翼则认为，任何协议都将有助于激励哈马斯。如果内塔尼亚胡和他的部长们考虑到这些困境就好了</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 07:32:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/how-israeli-hostages-became-pawns-in-an-ugly-political-game/00000191-75a1-d189-adbb-7dad718a0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么现在与真主党的停火协议对以色列不利</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-a-cease-fire-deal-with-hezbollah-now-is-bad-for-israel/00000191-7412-db7d-a7d7-7c9af4eb0000</link><description>正如国际调解人所希望的那样，将加沙和黎巴嫩的停战协议联系起来，将使主张消除主义的真主党取得宣传胜利，并对以色列的威慑和防御造成危险的影响</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 05:39:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-a-cease-fire-deal-with-hezbollah-now-is-bad-for-israel/00000191-7412-db7d-a7d7-7c9af4eb0000</guid></item><item><title>一个新的危险阶段：以色列与哈马斯未能达成协议将加剧中东地区更广泛冲突的风险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/failure-to-reach-hostage-deal-risks-wider-iran-hezbollah-response/00000191-769c-db30-a797-7ede7d000000</link><description>美国最近对确保停火的乐观态度可能被夸大了。虽然布林肯的出席确保真主党或伊朗不会在民主党全国代表大会期间对以色列进行报复，但情报显示黎巴嫩武装分子决心很快发动报复袭击。在华盛顿，希望奇迹至少还能再持续一天</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 03:00:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/failure-to-reach-hostage-deal-risks-wider-iran-hezbollah-response/00000191-769c-db30-a797-7ede7d000000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队：从加沙打捞的六名人质尸体上发现“枪声”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article-live/white-house-biden-stressed-urgency-of-sealing-gaza-deal-in-conversation-with-netanyahu/00000191-77df-dacb-afb3-ffffd81d0000</link><description>以色列军队：从加沙打捞上来的 6 名人质尸体上发现“枪声” ■ 涉嫌虐待巴勒斯坦被拘留者的士兵软禁延长两周 ■ 以色列国防军称从黎巴嫩发射的反坦克导弹在梅图拉爆炸，造成财产损失 ■ 以色列坦克深入加沙，巴勒斯坦人报告过去一天有 22 人丧生</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 02:38:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article-live/white-house-biden-stressed-urgency-of-sealing-gaza-deal-in-conversation-with-netanyahu/00000191-77df-dacb-afb3-ffffd81d0000</guid></item><item><title>美国以色列人质赫什·戈德堡-波林的父母向《国土报》表示：我们对民主党全国委员会的积极接待感到震惊</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/parents-of-u-s-israeli-hostage-to-haaretz-were-overwhelmed-by-positive-reception-at-dnc/00000191-77d8-dc26-a9d7-f7d9ca870001</link><description>乔恩·波林 (Jon Polin) 和雷切尔·戈德堡 (Rachel Goldberg) 的儿子赫什 (Hersh) 于 10 月 7 日被绑架，他们在民主党全国代表大会上发表讲话，高呼“带他们回家”</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 02:32:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/parents-of-u-s-israeli-hostage-to-haaretz-were-overwhelmed-by-positive-reception-at-dnc/00000191-77d8-dc26-a9d7-f7d9ca870001</guid></item><item><title>在民主党全国委员会拒绝给巴勒斯坦裔美国发言人时间后，“不承诺”举行静坐抗议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/minnesota-ag-ellison-vocal-critic-of-israel-tells-dnc-harris-is-listening-to-us-on-gaza/00000191-77bc-dacb-afb3-ffbfa3fa0000</link><description>明尼苏达州州长基思·埃里森（Keith Ellison）直言不讳地批评以色列，他告诉代表们，“卡马拉·哈里斯在加沙问题上正在倾听我们的意见”，随后引发抗议。</description><pubDate>Thu, 22 Aug 2024 01:45:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-22/ty-article/.premium/minnesota-ag-ellison-vocal-critic-of-israel-tells-dnc-harris-is-listening-to-us-on-gaza/00000191-77bc-dacb-afb3-ffbfa3fa0000</guid></item></channel></rss>